          <div class="content">
            <div class="content margin-bottom-20">
              <h2 class="has-text-centered-mobile">What are the benefits of renting?</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="flex-list box">
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Earn money from unused domains.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Organically grow traffic from your renters.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
