                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Increase the likelihood of a sale.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div> -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium has-border-bottom d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-3">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">How it works.</h1>
            <%# <p>
              Our platform introduces your domain to potential renters. We create the listing page,
              set rental terms, manage payments and transactions, and handle the process of
              redirecting renter's content to the domain. This process is detailed below.
            </p>%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe hiw">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step One</p>
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >You List Your Domain</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              Create custom listings using our upload tool and verify that you own them
              by pointing a DNS A Record to DomaHub.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe hiw">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Two</p>
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >Someone Rents It</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              We pay you directly into a bank account you've linked
              with us. Rentals are not complete until we confirm payment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe hiw">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Three</p>
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-share-square-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >We Redirect Web Content</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              The renter provides a link to some web content they wish to display and it is
              displayed on your domain for the duration of the rental.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
          <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Why list with DomaHub?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-server"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text margin-bottom-0">
                <h2>Never transfer domains</h2>
                <p>
                  You keep your nameservers.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  You maintain legal ownership of your domain. The renter does not use
                  their own nameservers.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-gears"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text margin-bottom-0">
                <h2>Control pricing and scheduling</h2>
                <p>
                  You have full control over both.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  You decide pricing for all of your domains.
                  You also decide the time it is available for: daily, weekly, or monthly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text margin-bottom-0">
                <h2>Quick and easy payments</h2>
                <p>
                  Get paid immediately and securely.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  Secured payment directly into your bank
                  account within a few business days.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text margin-bottom-0">
                <h2>Secure rental contracts</h2>
                <p>
                  All rentals are bounded by our terms.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  Every rental is subject to our <a href="/terms" class="is-accent">Terms</a>.
                  We reserve the right to remove any inappropriate rental on DomaHub.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="want-domains-section" class="section is-medium has-border-bottom d-renter is-hidden">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Our Benefits</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box dom-ben">
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-pie-chart"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >Affordable Prices</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              Exceptional domains can be expensive to buy, we know.
              Rentals are a cost-effective way to utilize the
              domains that you want!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box dom-ben">
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >Flexible Scheduling</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              Domains are available by the day, week or month. We work hard to make sure our domains
              fit your schedule perfectly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box dom-ben">
            <div class="flex-align-center">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-folder-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h2 >Exceptional Inventory</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              If a domain you want is not listed on DomaHub, we will do our best to get that domain for you!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium has-border-bottom d-renter is-hidden">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-3">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Using your domain rental.</h1>
            <%# <p>
              Every domain listing on DomaHub has verified demographics data and traffic statistics.
              We provide you with all the information you need to make an informed decision. Find a
              unique domain name that not only delivers the right message, but also has the exact
              audience you're looking to target.
            </p>%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
              <div class="content box has-stripe options">
                <p class="is-blacklight">
                  Option One
                </p>
                <div class="flex-align-center">
                  <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                    <i class="fa fa-television"></i>
                  </span>
                  <h2 >Display custom content.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>
                  Link web content (e.g. an image, GIF, or website) to your new rental.
                  Visitors to the rented domain will see your content for the duration of
                  your rental.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-5">
              <div class="content box has-stripe options">
                <p class="is-blacklight">
                  Option Two
                </p>
                <div class="flex-align-center">
                  <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                    <i class="fa fa-share"></i>
                  </span>
                  <h2 >Forward to another website.</h2>
                </div>
                <p>
                  Visitors to the rented domain will be forwarded to a website of your choosing.
                  You keep your existing brand and gain extra traffic from your new domain rental.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-renter is-hidden">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content margin-bottom-30">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">How it works.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4 is-offset-2">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>1. Browse Domains</h2>
            <p>
              Find a memorable domain name that fits your needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <figure class="image has-shadow is-real-ratio">
            <img src="/images/main/listing-capture.png" alt="Domain name rental listing page"/>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4 is-offset-2">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>2. Select Dates</h2>
            <p>
              Confirm your rental dates directly on the listing's page.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <figure class="image has-shadow is-real-ratio">
            <img src="/images/main/date-selection.gif" alt="Domain name rental date selection" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4 is-offset-2">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>3. Redirect Content</h2>
            <p>
              Provide a link to whatever web content you wish to redirect to your new domain
              rental.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <figure class="image-stack">
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-3.jpg" alt="Example website" />
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-2.jpg" alt="Example website" />
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-1.jpg" alt="Example website" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium has-pyramid is-primary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="content has-text-centered">
            <h1 class="title is-2 is-white">Have any questions?</h1>
            <h3 class="is-white">
              Feel free to send us a message or explore the FAQ!
            </h3>
            <div class="button-wrapper">
              <a tabindex="0" class="button is-primary is-inverted is-stylish" href="/contact" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <span class="icon">
                  <i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Contact Us</span>
              </a>
              <a tabindex="0" class="button is-accent is-stylish" href="/faq" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <span class="icon">
                  <i class="fa fa-question-circle-o"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Explore FAQ</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

